  "keyFeatures": [
    "Standard, Scientific, and Programmer calculator modes",
    "Date calculation with date difference and add/subtract operations",
    "Unit converter supporting multiple measurement categories",
    "Currency conversion with real-time exchange rates from Bing",
    "Infinite precision arithmetic for basic operations",
    "Calculation history and memory capabilities",
    "Graphing calculator functionality (UI available, engine mock in dev builds)",
    "XAML-based UWP application with MVVM architecture"
